24:24.130 --> 24:28.501
Aww, I'll never be swoll enough
to win back my wife.

24:28.501 --> 24:30.136
I miss you, Diana.

24:30.136 --> 24:33.205
I hope Todd breaches for you,
like I used to.

24:33.205 --> 24:36.208
I hope Todd
gives her life "porpoise."

